		function livefyreReplacer(element, count) {
			if(0 < count) {
				element.innerHTML = count;
				element.parentElement.className += ' has-comments';
			}
		}

			if(!window.LF || 'function' !== typeof window.LF.CommentCount) {
				return;
			}

			var lfArticles = window.LF.CommentCount.defaults.get_articles();
			var lfArticlesList = window.LF.CommentCount.helpers.articles_object_to_list(lfArticles);

				var loopArticleList = lfArticlesList.slice(0, articlesPerRequest);
				lfArticlesList = lfArticlesList.slice(articlesPerRequest);
				window.LF.CommentCount({
					articles: loopArticleList,
					replacer: livefyreReplacer
				});
			}

			if (0 < lfArticlesList.length) {
				window.LF.CommentCount({
					articles: lfArticlesList,
					replacer: livefyreReplacer
				});
			}
		};

	})();

	window.LFCommentCount();
	});
